originalText.text: My weight loss journey was phenomenal. I am glad that I got the opportunity to loose weight and get transformed under your guidance. Anshul Sir & Kinshuk Ma'am you guys are the best trainers. You never let me encounter any kind of dietary or physical issue. Proper schedule of everything and if any query, they had a solution to every issue. Amazingly approchable, always kept me motivated and supported throughout. Taught me how to stay healthy and what actually being healthy is meant to be. Honestly, I feel blessed that I consulted you guys.

originalText.text:
Anshul and Kinshuk have given me help and guidance along my journey of weight loss. I remember when I claimed that I have been through yoyo of weight loss and weight gain a lot of time due to PCOS, Anshul ensured me that they both will be my last nutrition coach, as I would not need one after that. And the way they both have guided me throughout keeps up with his word. When I started keto with both of them my only goal was to get back to regular periods by losing some weight. And I never imagined that I could achieve that with such busy schedule and minimal exercising. The diet they both guided me with worked like magic. Because of my body and hormone, weight loss was not a smooth process, but, they both understood what works best for me and helped me accordingly.

Today my weight is 65 kg (lost 17 kgs) and it is for the first time in my life that I am experiencing perfectly regular periods with 28 days cycle without any kind of medication. I have lost weight before as well, but, that never lead to regular periods. But this time it happened. Every time my periods starts, I feel so grateful. I am sure kinshuk completely understands what I am feeling.

They both were soo accommodating when I felt like having a break from the diet and resume back after a month.

Also, Along with providing diet with measurement of food, they both also helped me to understand how to be more aware of the macros I eat and how to convert grams of oil to grams of butter and importance of protein in my diet. I am confident now that I will be able to maintain my weight for a very long run as I have awareness of what to eat and what to avoid. Even if I am out on a trip, I am more mindful with what I consume, also I have the knowledge of how to recover after having cheat meal and all of that science behind sustainable weight maintenance.

Theier help with gradually getting out of ketogenic diet into a more sustainable (complex carb) diet for me is also much appreciated.

From a very happy and satisfied client!

originalText.text:
My reason to reach out to Firefueled LLC simply stemmed from a desire to be healthy. With unpredictable work hours, I was showing signs of PCOD & thyroid which worried me.

Anshul was my obvious go-to choice for this because of the endless, personal testimonies I had been hearing about him since my college years. And it really couldn't have been better. Personal, motivating and engaging - this program had everything I was looking for.

Few points that stood out for me personally:
1. Every phase of the program was planned keeping my schedule and availability in mind. Anshul ensured that even when my pre-planned schedule was disrupted (COVID lockdown, work related travel), I did not lose any progress made.
2. With the expectation to be hands-on in my meal preps (and me not being particularly gifted in the kitchen!), Anshul took the time to chalk out easy and fun recipes, without me breaking a sweat.
3. Having a 2nd coach in Kinshuk helped address untimely queries. (And her motivation boosters were added bonus!)
4. Most importantly, Anshul took the time out to explain the science behind every process that I came across as part of my plan. I am now more aware and better equipped to take care of myself going forward.

I'll always be grateful for this incredible journey. Thank you!

originalText.text: A fitness trainer who aims not only to make you fit but to make you aware about your body and what drives it in all respect. One of the best motivators as well - I was going through a lot in my personal life as well along with a bad physical shape and Anshul made sure that my stress isn't hindering my fitness journey. Anyone who's looking for a lifestyle coach should certainly knock once on Anshul's door.

originalText.text:
Training with firefueled fitness has given me a better insight of not only just about fitness and muscle building but also about nutrition which plays a major role in our daily life.
Anshul created a customized diet and workout plan based on your targets and daily activity to match your activity be it a slow or busy lifestyle.
Before we began he patiently explained the process that body goes through during the adoption and continuation of a ketogenic lifestyle.
He asked for a constant feedback and made changes to my plan during my weight stall phase (weight plateau)
His constant motivation combined with his cook book and a custom diet and workout plan together helped me in reaching my target.
I highly recommend training with firefueled fitness
